# API Generator - Harita Hive Enterprise Tool
# MIT License
#
# Auto-generates secure APIs for any uploaded geospatial file
# Includes authentication and rate limiting
#
# Features:
# - Automatic API generation from geospatial files
# - RESTful and GraphQL endpoint support
# - Built-in authentication (JWT, OAuth2, API keys)
# - Rate limiting and quota management
# - Automatic documentation generation
# - CORS and security headers
#
# Supported Input Formats:
# - Shapefiles, GeoJSON, KML
# - PostGIS database tables
# - GeoTIFF raster files
# - CSV with coordinate columns
#
# Generated Endpoints:
# - GET /features (list all features)
# - GET /features/{id} (get specific feature)
# - POST /features (create new feature)
# - PUT /features/{id} (update feature)
# - DELETE /features/{id} (delete feature)
# - GET /spatial/intersects (spatial queries)
#
# Security Features:
# - Rate limiting (requests per minute/hour)
# - IP whitelisting/blacklisting
# - Data encryption in transit
# - Input validation and sanitization
#
# Usage:
# api-generator --input dataset.shp --name "Properties API" --auth jwt
# api-generator --postgis --table parcels --rate-limit 1000/hour